Package peril.ai.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Army
    Provides information about a army consisting of Units.
    Board
    Provides information about the board which consists of many Continents and Countrys.
    Continent
    Provides information about a continent on the Board that consists of many Countrys.
    Country
    Provides the information of a country.
    Player
    Provides information about a player.
    Points
    Provides the point reward values of given actions in the game.
    Unit
    Provides information about a unit.
